  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nIn mainnet node it could take up to 0.5s to `recomputeForkChoiceHead`\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1085\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-06 at 15 10 27\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/f23cce32-037a-4649-946d-4fce2eb27229\">\r\n\r\nand it takes 6% of cpu in total\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1314\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-06 at 15 22 50\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/262bfb37-e9d5-42e9-8b09-2d56a1b076ee\">\r\n\r\nwhile out benchmark says <= 100ms\r\n\r\nsee https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/5836#issuecomment-1666767135\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nGet back to the level of v1.9.x\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1298\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-06 at 15 12 01\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/0357c7e4-92bc-442e-9852-dd321ac937e9\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Operating system\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\r\n\r\nv1.10.0",
